    upload() {
      let data = this.data.url; // （data/image）:数据
      console.log(data)
      this.sumitImageFile(data);
    },

    /**
     * @param base64Codes
     *            图片的base64编码
     */
    sumitImageFile(base64Codes) {
      var formData = new FormData(); 

      //convertBase64UrlToBlob函数是将base64编码转换为Blob
      formData.append("fileFolder", this.convertBase64UrlToBlob(base64Codes)); 
        
      var api =
        "/coral-base/api/coral/base/archive/fileUpload/uploadScanDaFiles?idCardNum=411325198607257955";
      this.axios
        .post(api, formData)
        .then(res => {
          if (res.data.success) {
            console.log("上传成功");
          }
        })
        .catch(error => {
          console.log(error);
        });
    },

    /**
     * 将以base64的图片url数据转换为Blob
     * @param urlData
     *            用url方式表示的base64图片数据
     */

    convertBase64UrlToBlob(urlData) {
      var bytes = window.atob(urlData.split(",")[1]); //去掉url的头，并转换为byte

      //处理异常,将ascii码小于0的转换为大于0
      var ab = new ArrayBuffer(bytes.length);
      var ia = new Uint8Array(ab);
      for (var i = 0; i < bytes.length; i++) {
        ia[i] = bytes.charCodeAt(i);
      }

      return new Blob([ab], { type: "image/png" });
    },
